=pick(match(v_ViewUptake & '_' & v_ViewTargetGroup, 'FIRST_80', 'SECOND_80', 'FIRST_70', 'SECOND_70', 'FIRST_60', 'SECOND_60', 'ADD_60', 'FIRST_50', 'SECOND_50', 'FIRST_HCW', 'SECOND_HCW', 'FIRST_LTCF', 'SECOND_LTCF'),

'Cumulative uptake (%) of at least one vaccine dose among people aged 80 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of full vaccination among people aged 80 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of at least one vaccine dose among people aged 70 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of full vaccination among people aged 70 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of at least one vaccine dose among people aged 60 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of full vaccination among people aged 60 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of additional doses among people aged 60 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of at least one vaccine dose among people aged 50 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of full vaccination among people aged 50 years and above in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of at least one vaccine dose among healthcare workers in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of full vaccination among healthcare workers in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of at least one vaccine dose among LTCF residents in ',
'Cumulative uptake (%) of full vaccination among LTCF residents in '
) 
& [Member State]
& ' as of '& date(ReloadTime(), 'YYYY-MM-DD')

byMeasureDef.label: =[Member State]
byMeasureDef.key:
pick(match(v_ViewUptake & '_' & v_ViewTargetGroup , 'FIRST_80', 'SECOND_80', 'FIRST_HCW', 'SECOND_HCW', 'FIRST_LTCF', 'SECOND_LTCF'),
 	rangemin( 1, sum({$*<[MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}>} Uptake1st_80_Cumul) ),
	rangemin( 1, sum({$*<[MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}>} Uptake2nd_80_Cumul) ),
    rangemin( 1, sum({$*<[MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}>} Uptake1st_HCW_Cumul) ),
    rangemin( 1, sum({$*<[MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}>} Uptake2nd_80_Cumul) ),
    rangemin( 1, sum({$*<[MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}>} Uptake1st_LTCF_Cumul) ),
    rangemin( 1, sum({$*<[MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}>} Uptake2nd_LTCF_Cumul) ) 
)
